-- British Film Director Bryan Forbes Dies at 86, PA Reports
-- B y   M i k e   H a r r i s o n
-- 2013-05-09T07:29:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-09/british-film-director-bryan-forbes-dies-at-86-pa-reports.html
British film director Bryan Forbes has
died following a long illness, the Press Association said,
citing family friend Matthew D’Ancona. He was 86.  Forbes, whose films include The Stepford Wives, King Rat
and Whistle Down The Wind, died yesterday at his home in Surrey,
England, PA cited D’Ancona as saying.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
